kelmore5.java.yeh.data_structures.node

Class LinkedNode<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • kelmore5.java.yeh.data_structures.node.Node<T>
      • kelmore5.java.yeh.data_structures.node.LinkedNode<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type parameter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DoubleLinkedNode

    public class LinkedNode<T>
extends Node<T>
     A linked node is a node used in a linked list. It only has a datum and next node parameter.
 A linked node uses the next parameter to link to the next nodes in a list.
    Date:
    Fall 2012
